{"type":"message","id":"77194a80","parentId":"cb2e4f02","timestamp":"2026-03-24T20:09:44.073Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_nmiqtcl2jmnb_2","toolName":"process","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[LLM] response length: 5337\r\n[mutation parsed via Python] old='(new file)' file='' new_len=3083\r\n[file inferred from ACTION] a\r\n[mutation proposed] a\r\n[master ed9bfd3] pulse: 2026-03-24 160909\n 5 files changed, 298 insertions(+), 72 deletions(-)\n create mode 100644 memory/session/pulse_2026-03-24 160909.md\n create mode 100644 mutations/proposed/2026-03-24 160909.mutation\n[sandbox pulse] 2026-03-24 160909 - The CFI analysis is complete, but we still need empirical evidence distinguishing Pattern Information (CFI) from true Causal Information. The Conditional Content Analysis experiment is the critical next step to resolve this.\r\n\n\nProcess exited with code 0."}],"details":{"status":"completed","sessionId":"swift-nudibranch","exitCode":0,"aggregated":"[LLM] response length: 5337\r\n[mutation parsed via Python] old='(new file)' file='' new_len=3083\r\n[file inferred from ACTION] a\r\n[mutation proposed] a\r\n[master ed9bfd3] pulse: 2026-03-24 160909\n 5 files changed, 298 insertions(+), 72 deletions(-)\n create mode 100644 memory/session/pulse_2026-03-24 160909.md\n create mode 100644 mutations/proposed/2026-03-24 160909.mutation\n[sandbox pulse] 2026-03-24 160909 - The CFI analysis is complete, but we still need empirical evidence distinguishing Pattern Information (CFI) from true Causal Information. The Conditional Content Analysis experiment is the critical next step to resolve this.\r\n","name":"C:\\Users\\Zwmar\\.openclaw\\sandbox\\pulse.ps1"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1774382984069}}
